{"word":"στιγμή","slug":"στιγμή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στιγμή</b></el> <el>(στιγμή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στίζω'><el>στίζω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:στίγμα'><el>στίγμα</el></a>\n<p/><i>a spot, point</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>:— <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>a jot, tittle</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; <el>ἐν στ. χρόνου</el> in <i>a moment</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}